                     <interp inst="t18470201-554-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 2 spoons, value 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18470201-name-559" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18470201-name-559" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
