                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman 10 F.</hi>) I produced a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction.—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted April 1845, in the name of Joseph Bennett, and confined four months</hi>)—he is the man—I saw him found guilty.</p>
               <p>(There were two other indictments against the prisoner.)</p>
